short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View codes for your favorite games directly on Roblox.com!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Roblox Den is one of the leading Roblox game codes websites and now we've packed all of that goodness into a Chrome extension, meaning you can get what you need without having to visit our website.

If you hate missing codes for your favorite Roblox experiences - and want to save time - then this extension is for you!

The Roblox Den Extension adds a codes preview box to Roblox.com when you're viewing a game that Roblox Den has available codes for. From here, you can easily copy codes to use in-game without having to search the web for codes.

Additionally, it highlights robloxden.com in Bing and Google so that you don't miss us! This feature can be turned off in the extension settings.
